      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2023-03-09</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2023-05-02T16:56:39Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;National Weather Service Communications Improvement Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the National Weather Service (NWS) to replace NWSChat with a commercial, off-the-shelf communications solution that is hosted on the public cloud. (NWSChat is an instant messaging program used by NWS personnel to share, in real-time, critical warnings and other types of weather information.) The NWS shall allocate up to $3 million of its funding for FY2024-FY2027 on the replacement.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
